  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育LMS门户的状态流转图。核心是从Education_LMS_Portal开始，用户刚进入时应该是Idle状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，入口指向Idle。那用户发起请求后进入什么状态？Loading吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Idle到Loading的触发条件是Start Request。Loading之后要分叉——成功的话到Success，失败的话到Error。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Start Request",
        "Data Received",
        "Request Failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。Loading到Success标注Data Received，Loading到Error标注Request Failed。Success和Error之后都能回到Idle吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Success回Idle用Reset，这个没问题。但Error回Idle应该是Retry，而且Error还要有一条终止路径——直接连到Education_ClassroomService，标注Abort。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Retry",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊，我刚才漏掉了Abort那条线。现在补上：Error到Education_ClassroomService是Abort，Error到Idle是Retry。检查一遍，Idle、Loading、Success、Error四个状态，入口是Education_LMS_Portal，终止可以连到Education_ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
